\begin_layout Standard
When observers are asked to detect weak broadband motion signals in noise,
 they can integrate localized motion signals over relatively large regions
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Williams:1984aa,Downing:1989aa,Fredericksen:1994wv"

\end_inset

