\begin_layout Standard
Another possibility is that first-order motion in my stimuli is integrated
 across space as a kind of contour integration.
 Detection of a motion element is facilitated when it aligns in direction
 and position with another moving element 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Verghese:2000aa,Verghese:2002aa"

\end_inset

