reference "mov:demo"

\end_inset

, I started pilot experiments which followed a simple procedure: using stimuli
 with fixed carrier strength and envelope motion, I asked observers to report
 the apparent direction of motion while varying the inter-element spacing.
 I expected that when putting carrier and envelope motion in conflict, apparent
