 of visual crowding.
 However, only some observers showed equivocation by this procedure; others
 appeared to correctly classify the direction of motion regardless of spacing.
 After trying a stimulus with zero envelope motion it turned out that these
 observers had been responding not to envelope motion but 
\emph on
against 
\emph default
carrier motion.
