\begin_layout Standard
Eventually I tried following the advice of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citeauthor
key "Pelli:2008ao"

\end_inset

 (
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citeyear
key "Pelli:2008ao"

\end_inset

, supplementary material) who suggested that measurements of crowding phenomena
