 Thus some forms of induced motion might be accounted for by a subtractive
 interaction between first-order and positional motion mechanisms, rather
 than as a center-surround interaction.
 Still it is likely that 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

induced motion
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 encompasses several different effects; there are also variants of induced
